## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="22d83-140">在下列範例中，方法會傳回包含已辨識片語的語意的 SML 的字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-140">In the following example, a method returns a string that contains the SML for the semantics of a recognized phrase.</span></span>  
  
```  
private string GetSemanticsSML(RecognizedPhrase result)  
{  
  if (result.Semantics.Count > 0)  
  {  
    return result.ConstructSmlFromSemantics().CreateNavigator().OuterXml;  
  }  
  else  
  {  
    return null;  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="22d83-161">語音辨識文法可以包含語意資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-161">A speech recognition grammar can include semantic information.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="22d83-162">當語音辨識器產生這類文法的辨識結果時，語意資訊可能會包含在辨識結果中，根據規則的文法和辨識器的輸入。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-162">When a speech recognizer generates a recognition result for such a grammar, the semantic information might be included in the recognition result, according to the rules of the grammar and the input to the recognizer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="22d83-163">如需有關語意資訊的詳細資訊，請參閱[了解語意結果](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2a9dbd8b-cf6d-42cd-bbb9-ca0b3e534005)並<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>和<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>類別。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-163">For more information about semantic information, see [Understanding Semantic Results](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/2a9dbd8b-cf6d-42cd-bbb9-ca0b3e534005) and the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue> classes.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="22d83-164">下列範例會定義方法，以取得從已辨識片語的語意的特定資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-164">The following example defines a method that gets specific semantic information from a recognized phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="22d83-165">當這個方法傳回時，它包含語意索引鍵，則為 null 的值，如果不擷取的值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-165">When this method returns, it contains the value for the semantic key, or null if the value was not retrieved.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="22d83-166">這個方法只會檢查最上層機碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-166">This method checks only for top-level keys.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="22d83-167">因為語意資訊包含在樹狀目錄中的值時，較低層級金鑰必須透過傳回的語意值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="22d83-167">Since the semantic information is contained in a tree of values, lower-level keys must be accessed through the returned semantic value.</span></span>  
  
```  
static bool TryGetSemanticValue(  
      RecognizedPhrase phrase, string key, out SemanticValue value)  
{  
  value = null;  
  bool found = phrase.Semantics.ContainsKey(key);  
  if (found)  
  {  
    value = phrase.Semantics[key];  
  }  
  
  return found;  
}  
```
